    "date": "2023-04-14T15:52:55Z",
    "text": "Defund Heroin Injection Centers Act of 2023\n\nThis bill prohibits federal funds from being made available to a state, local, tribal, or private entity that operates or controls an injection center (i.e., a medically supervised injection site) in violation of the federal statute commonly known as the Crack House Statute. The statute generally prohibits making facilities available for the purpose of unlawfully using a controlled substance."
